posts.title: Charles Horton Cooley
posts.body: I am not what I think I am, and I am not what you think I am. I am what I think you think I am.

posts.title: Aristotle
posts.body: Quality is not an act, it is a habit.

posts.title: Jen Sincero
posts.body: Worrying is like praying for something That you don't want.
